{"tid":2450102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批評習近平！中國「大五毛」網紅喝醉 直播崩潰大罵共產黨","createTime":"2021-03-17T06:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T22:06:53.000Z","uid":337052,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"17b87737312fef37b506ab494ef982650a3c49ab","tid":2450102,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">批評習近平！中國「大五毛」網紅喝醉 直播崩潰大罵共產黨</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/16/phpfyD4AE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2FphpfyD4AE.jpg&h=18399a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭國成因東北老家遭貪官侵占，日前邊直播邊喝酒，喝醉後罕見地在直播中大罵共產黨。（擷取自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n2021/03/17 00:09<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">中國網紅鄭國成在YouTube擁有超過10萬人追蹤，他除了時常發表「愛黨」言論，也曾拍片胡扯前桃園市議員王浩宇是總統蔡英文、前總統李登輝的私生子。他也因為這些離譜言論，被自家網友封為「油管（YouTube）大五毛」。近日，他的東北老家遭貪官侵占，日前邊直播邊喝酒，喝醉後罕見地在直播中大罵共產黨。</span><br />\n<br />\n鄭國成除了有YouTube頻道，也同時經營中國B站（哔哩哔哩）、微博、知乎等社群平台。他的YouTube頻道上傳影片中，針對反送中、中澳貿易、中印邊境衝突等國際事件頻頻替中國發聲，並批評其他國家，點閱最高的則是標題「王浩宇是蔡英文和李登輝的私生子，陳水扁幫忙拉皮條，震撼台灣2300萬人」的影片。看不慣鄭國成言行的人，因此稱他為「油管（YouTube）大五毛」，批他「翻牆發舔共影片為生」。<br />\n<br />\n鄭國成近日指控，東北老家林地遭到當地貪官侵占，上訪無門。3月11日，他喝醉直播，過程中大罵共產黨，痛批上訪制度根本沒道理，他不但稱中國都是貪官汙吏，還大肆批評中共種種制度：「你天天批判西方，自己做不到有什麼資格批判別人！」、「天天喊中國牛了、中國牛B有什麼用？」<br />\n<br />\n直播過程中，有其他網友CALL IN勸他冷靜，鄭國成卻越來越激動，一下大罵國家欺壓人民，甚至指沒解決問題，領導人（習近平）要下台，期間，他更自爆：<span class=\"red\">「我打扮成愛國青年，上個月我賺了7000多美元」</span>，還稱所有將親屬移民到歐美等國家的人，都應該被誅九族。種種言論讓不少中國網友相當錯愕。<br />\n<br />\n事後，鄭國成已經將當天直播刪除，另外也發布道歉影片，自稱發表了一些「極端言論」，影響到一直熱愛他的粉絲，他心裡也非常難受。他解釋，近日家裡發生許多不好的事情，讓他喝了許多酒，才導致這些極端言論，對於網友的批評，他虛心接受，也要向大家道歉，保證以後不會發生類似事情。<br />\n<br />\n對此，不少網友在YouTube相關影片下方留言，「妄議中央、尋釁滋事」、「現在覺得他好可怕」、「台媒只要大肆渲染這個事情，他就完蛋了」、「鄭國成精神有問題」、「他那是酒後的直播！不用過分解讀！」、「鄭應該去法院起訴，他想用輿論影響司法，有違法制精神」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/16/phpnUuXSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2FphpnUuXSB.jpg&h=f5cdccc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在其頻道中，點閱最高的則是一部標題「王浩宇是蔡英文和李登輝的私生子，陳水扁幫忙拉皮條，震撼台灣2300萬人」的影片。（擷取自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3469109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3469109&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=d95ca05d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3469109&h=faf907cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3469109</a>"},{"pid":"c438f4fae07a1512f6e744d619a45523724216be","tid":2450102,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eLL72mtrfyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeLL72mtrfyQ&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=246403c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eLL72mtrfyQ</a><br />\n「大五毛」鄭國成罵黨罵習的備分檔"},{"pid":"759c78bc210b78ca973cde65802beb993cd9e91d","tid":2450102,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TLsOkJfWS6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTLsOkJfWS6c&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=45e53371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TLsOkJfWS6c</a><br />\n「大五毛」的道歉"},{"pid":"295193570e6ae7c8efac04293b929d254b51e98d","tid":2450102,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p4utfkUo-Fw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp4utfkUo-Fw&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=131f8c74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p4utfkUo-Fw</a>"},{"pid":"20db0ee2084a696d2dfd1c5951a549fb1f0cc14f","tid":2450102,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:02:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OFlqzCLUN9U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOFlqzCLUN9U&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=b181e2e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OFlqzCLUN9U</a>"},{"pid":"2f1b502d39b17a56fa6b40c54e1a36ace8789ff4","tid":2450102,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b653fe4acd8bae0256df456c49206c1576a622d","tid":2450102,"uid":37413,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"已用了人生唯一一次言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939b3bd1f0de86850923794578000606c16bff21","tid":2450102,"uid":89184,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"係中國講&ldquo;有違法制精神&ldquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0d36de4ae0161b75fd4fb41ad68ee5472234a6","tid":2450102,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5b653fe4acd8bae0256df456c49206c1576a622d","tid":2450102,"uid":37413,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"已用了人生唯一一次言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"我們懷念他"},{"pid":"32a2453ce8712f48b60f8addcdee685f7e0e616b","tid":2450102,"uid":89184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"其實佢識玩，如袁大帥一樣，收回"},{"pid":"2a8c3d0ceda329c6d741e357ce029a01ed4d8376","tid":2450102,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"油管 YouTube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc655874c15986b164796db8bd897d106dd96b6","tid":2450102,"uid":56999,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZvNCSDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvNCSDE.jpg&h=9c4bbe4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"461008be1158fcff56cfb2ee0fb4b624eaf56254","tid":2450102,"uid":394010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"支那五毛抵撚死啦"},{"pid":"66fab067255f1df784ae21ac2379015ea3c031e3","tid":2450102,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">活膩了？大陸網紅喝醉開直播 譙共產黨「領導人下台」</span></strong><br />\n2021/03/17 12:39 東森新聞 責任編輯 林承峰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2021/03/17/1615984955_82748.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F1615984955_82748.jpg&h=110781e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國大陸一名網紅，過去時常拍影片發表熱愛共產黨的言論，也曾經拿總統蔡英文來開玩笑，引起熱烈討論。沒想到近日老家遭貪官侵占，他竟然邊開直播邊喝酒，最後不勝酒力，開始在鏡頭前痛批共產黨，甚至直接喊出「領導人下台！」<br />\n<br />\n網紅鄭國成在YouTube擁有10.5萬名粉絲追蹤，他時常針對議題性的話題發出影片，像是過去就PO過有關香港反送中、中印邊境衝突等的國際事件，其中點閱最高的影片是，「王浩宇是蔡英文和李登輝的私生子，陳水扁幫忙拉皮條，震撼台灣2300萬人」，目前已經累計57萬人觀看，讓不少網友看了狂喊，「你掌握『自由』的真諦」、「太勁爆了！這個有創意」、「被你這麼一說，我真是有點相信了」。<br />\n<br />\n▼鄭國成過去發表有關蔡英文的影片，引起熱烈討論。（圖／翻攝自中國青年鄭國成YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2021/03/17/1615985048_81493.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F1615985048_81493.jpg&h=9b2bc9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒想到，鄭國成11日卻因為喝醉，開始在直播鏡頭前透露位在東北的老家，被當地貪官侵占，接著開始痛批共產黨制度沒有道理，「你天天批判西方，自己做不到有什麼資格批判別人！」並自爆打扮成愛國青年，上個月就賺了7000元美金（約新台幣20萬），他更是在直播過程直接點名領導人沒有解決問題就下台，一番言論讓不少網友致電請他冷靜，不少人看了都感到相當傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n鄭國成酒醒後立刻將直播刪除，並隨即發布一支道歉影片，為自己發表的極端言論感到抱歉，面對大家的批評，鄭國成表示都會虛心接受，承諾未來不會再發生類似的事情，不過網友仍留言嗆，「刪的還挺快，不過我們都保存了，會給親愛的黨媽媽看的」、「鄭公公，早就知道你是真正的反黨人士了，終於露餡了」、「終於！超級愛國的！我有下載！真是棒棒的影片！保重了」、「跪是一種人生態度，舔是一項生活技巧。」<br />\n<br />\n▼鄭國成的道歉影片引起網友熱烈討論。（圖／翻攝自中國青年鄭國成YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2021/03/17/1615985324_85280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F1615985324_85280.jpg&h=9edf2880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/news/world/253270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F253270&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=c12c7f61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/news/world/253270</a>"},{"pid":"9d0dca15e019d4a2ac88d4faa2aab411fb7467f8","tid":2450102,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"跪求backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7effa7b4feaaf9ded58cebe8b9c745f649780da4","tid":2450102,"uid":22554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d119404e1e66b3b326f33dc7459024c94ce735ad","tid":2450102,"uid":149844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c438f4fae07a1512f6e744d619a45523724216be","tid":2450102,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eLL72mtrfyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeLL72mtrfyQ&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=246403c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eLL72mtrfyQ</a><br />\n「大五毛」鄭國成罵黨罵習的備分檔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:41:11.000Z","msg":"Pin this<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src